         <abstract id="aspace_616b823ee79e6e26c0c362d00ef91462">Chiefly letters written to Pearson by friends and relatives. Includes correspondence (1804-1821) between Pearson and his father, Eliphalet Pearson, dealing with Henry's student days at Andover, Yale, and Harvard; and letters from Pearson to his sister Margaret Blanchard.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
